{"tid":998500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民譴責反水貨客示威","createTime":"2019-01-28T04:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T23:38:07.000Z","uid":53062,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cda7113ac667c20b118e4c15ed7b20ab41d7be43","tid":998500,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:35:14.000Z","msg":"泛民譴責反水貨客示威。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨何俊仁表示，示威衝擊的場面令人痛心，完全超越示威的界線。何俊仁期望，年青人反思這種手段，即使成功趕走水貨客，亦令全港受到傷害。<br />\n<br />\n香港本土成員毛孟靜譴責暴力，指示威者侮辱他人，只會弄巧反拙，令本土運動污名化，反對水貨活動的訴求變得模糊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/105234/a2-3@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F105234%2Fa2-3%401200x1200.jpg&h=92b9ebde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28511d5cdd99ab82162571069cfc0757a6bea998","tid":998500,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:40:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">賣港賊害港一例</span></span>"},{"pid":"81056da196b07324945fd980b01b831d35783467","tid":998500,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596a7e156441e2a91f1c8243e73d1872b4e8f29f","tid":998500,"uid":37612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:08:00.000Z","msg":"廢老又出黎"},{"pid":"f882f72ae16f1bda381abf6fff29730368d5a9dd","tid":998500,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:14:25.000Z","msg":"泛民主派想搞分裂， 擺明想畀位共產黨上， 泛民肯定係鬼"},{"pid":"a1e8405d40b7860ef01d08e742cbbb583b5a8240","tid":998500,"uid":43173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T23:05:05.000Z","msg":"示威定示弱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72ec06d60577f4a36375a650835fc9be22533ad","tid":998500,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T2